# Air Pollution Project Skopje

## Overview
This project analyzes air pollution data for multiple locations in Skopje, using CSV datasets for different pollutants (CO, NO2, O3, PM10, PM2.5). The analysis includes:

- Data cleaning and preprocessing  
- Extraction of year, month, day, and hour from timestamps  
- Handling missing values with mean imputation  
- Aggregation of pollution data by hour, day, month, and year  
- Visualization of pollution trends using bar charts and scatter plots  
- Identification of peak and lowest pollution periods  
- Comparison across multiple locations  

The project is implemented using **Python (pandas, numpy, matplotlib)**

